.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

The people's birthday is in 5 different months: june, february, august, may, october
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: lacrosse, badminton, tennis, rugby, snowboarding
House: modern, gothic-revival, farmhouse, futuristic, tower
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: junemaster, scientific, disaster, spy, epic
5 different games are played: mah-jongg, backgammon, go, whist, canasta
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person who's birthday is in august
2. the person who's sport is swedish is the person playing go
3. the person who's sport is badminton is the futuristic house
4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may
5. the person who's birthday is in february is the gothic-revival house
6. the person watching disaster movies is the person playing backgammon
7. the person who's birthday is in october is the person watching scientific movies
8. the farmhouse house is in the middle
9. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left
10. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg
11. the person playing canastas is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies
12. the person watching junemaster movies is the modern house
13. the person who's sport is tennis is the person watching spy movies
14. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june
15. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the tower house

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Birthday		|    october	|     june	|      august	|     february	|     may	|
| Sport	|   rugby	|    badminton	|    lacrosse	|    tennis	|    swedish	|
| Game		|     mah-jongg	|    canasta	|     backgammon	|     whist	|      go	|
| House	|    tower	|     futuristic	|     farmhouse	|    gothic-revival	|      modern	|
| Movie-Genre		|   scientific	|    epic	|  disaster	|    spy	|   junemaster	|
